Better Homes And Gardens Real Estate Main Street Properties

data.description: Don't miss this rare opportunity to own Lakefront Property in Pensacola at a price that won't break the bank!   This beloved, one owner home offers you an incredible mix of space and tranquility with many updates that have already been completed for you!   Step inside and you'll be captivated with a lakeview from almost every room and soaring ceilings! The Great Room features a gas fireplace and enough room for a full set of living room furniture and a grand piano.   The massive Kitchen is a show stopper that is equipped with ample cabinet and countertop space, kitchen island, and a breakfast nook area all freshly updated with BRAND NEW quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash and recently refurbished white cabinets.  The home also features a nicely sized formal dining room that is perfect for entertaining.  In addition to the 4 bedrooms, there is an enclosed office with custom built in bookshelves, making working from home a breeze!  Take full advantage of the lovely lake view with  the 324 Sq Ft Solarium that was added by the owners.  Other updates to note, Roof is 2023, Luxury Vinyl plank flooring added to common entertaining areas, Whole Home water purification system, and Irrigation System in Place to maintain over $10,000 worth of landscaping upgrades!
